हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description:
A forced marriage hides shocking secrets: the groom who appears poor is actually a secret billionaire. A mother’s desperate search for her lost twin children takes unexpected turns.
This is a story of hidden identities, betrayal, and an unexpected love born from lies.
